Ask HN: Am I Unhireable?
text:
Am I unhireable?

The reasons I ask: 17 years ago I was arrested for having intercourse with a minor, I technically wasn't convicted of a felony. I have no financial credit. I have no college degree. I have schizophrenia.

Long story short, I dedicated the past 15 years working for my family's business. I was responsible for new customer acquisition, marketing, lead gen, and business development. I've been programming since I was young, I'm efficient with Python.

I've started several companies that weren't profitable or scalable.

What would be my best path forward to securing consistent income and employment?
